Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, do whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I like Koizumi or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I hear that right, just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been rejected by the same guy twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:55.38,Title,,0,0,0,,Maity's Magic!\NThe Transforming Patterns of Love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko... Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I like Koizumi or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san, was that a snapping sound I heard just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity-sensei, you were so cool just now-chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Otani-san. Good work-chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But you seemed a bit out of it today-chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Koizumi. Just now, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going home-chi. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What have we got all wrong? Let's hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Everything's gone bad because that old man stuck his nose in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who blames his problems on others is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, where did Maity-sensei go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He went after Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I like Koizumi or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it all along, even without hearing him say it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back, I've been giving it everything I've got since last summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess it was all pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you were rejected once already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And that just now makes it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't let what Otani-kun said just now bother you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just his way of hiding his embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. What could he possibly have to hide or be embarrassed about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's clear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now I said, "I'll take Koizumi-san for myself," as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Otani-kun got angry and replied in that manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think he did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because he just doesn't like you, Maity-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I think I'll give being hated a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I know how to perform magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use my magic to bring you happiness, Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In that moment, I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Maity-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,M A I T Y Love Maity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently it's a cheer to support Maity-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right at this very moment, a frail maiden is having an audible breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All because of one cold man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Maity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Otani-kun here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on you at practice again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not feeling well like last time, just let me know, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I always give 100%! Just bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Well, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:07:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Koizumi-san to see my good side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,La, la...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That wonderful smile of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity, Maity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,La, la, la...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't concentrate with all that noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Let's cheer for Otani-san too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good to blame your problems on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you hurry and show me that determination of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san did come to cheer us on, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a way to show her my good side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to start a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity-sama will bring me happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to live my life seeing only Maity-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just Maity-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity... sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed a school bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you get on the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you quit that disgusting Maity Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind why, just quit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. And besides, it's my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's fine about it? What's with all that anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to provoke me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're a midget who always speaks without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the one who speaks without thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it that claimed to be in love, then gave up, then randomly blew me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I have to hear this from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pissed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was shocked to see you'd vanished all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. I'll drive you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll take Koizumi-san home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi just committed to taking me home on this bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? Didn't you just say you didn't need me to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, I'm the one Koizumi-san likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she'd fall for someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't just go saying things whenever you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like you, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I really have no idea what Otani's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Riding tandem is prohibited!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with those smiles you're wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard everything from Maity, Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani said something great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what's going on with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened when you took him home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he say anything? Did he confess to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! But he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm the one she likes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd like to know too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sigh when you see someone's face in the morning. It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well what do you expect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We were busted for riding tandem yesterday, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You were injured! It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be thanking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no... No, no... It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's emotionally unstable, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's definitely jealous because you're paying so much attention to Maity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Otani jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard him say he didn't like me, not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But wasn't that because Maity interfered?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I seriously have no idea what's up with Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani is... jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But up till now, every time I've gotten my hopes up, I've only been disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't expect thing to work out anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani, what are you going to do about club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just watch you guys practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There sure have been a lot of injuries lately.\NThe coach isn't better yet either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Otani-senpai is injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's only minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, Seiko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, but Otani-senpai is injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you worried, Koizumi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this odd atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say a word about it, Seiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are as clueless as baby fawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Seiko-chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...but something terrible has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-senpai is injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Klutz! You got yourself injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You lookin' for a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Risa, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ignoring me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You formed the Maity club, and held some events, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I like Maity a lot, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't I told you? Maity is my cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've liked him ever since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was always in Tokyo, so I didn't get to see him much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I was wondering why he's so irritating...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do mean, "irritating"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity is so much kinder and cooler than this midget that any comparison would be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going after Maity, you have my support.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you angry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your Maity club?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me to quit, so I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't you need me to chauffeur you to your abode again today, Otani-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that yesterday, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But then when Maity-sensei showed up, you were all, "Take me home!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you went on saying "I'm the one she likes,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...and other unnecessary stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end you dragged me away by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My fault! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go help pack up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for you by the front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I try, I have no idea what's going on in Otani's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want this weird atmosphere to hang around forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san's a nice girl, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to tell me. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are short, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill you! I'm gonna kill you!\NI'm seriously going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were a girl, I'm sure I wouldn't want such a short boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But Koizumi-san likes you anyway, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you really be okay with it if Koizumi-san goes out with someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, give Koizumi-san my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You were slow, so I came to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Hop on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I can peddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But your foot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your foot really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But the bike's going really slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you're heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually because you don't have enough strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary! Scary! Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fall! I'm gonna fall off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to laugh like an idiot with Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why things get weird once the idea of liking or disliking comes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If I never said that I liked him and just kept going like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...we could have stayed a comedy duo forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that would be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've been frustrated or upset because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...you don't need to worry about it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now I've said a lot of things that have bothered you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I won't say any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...for real this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really going to stop liking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:21:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes dried out so much just now that they're getting stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't keep them open.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't open my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, we really can go back to the way we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My last basketball match...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, are you gonna come to cheer me on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Give it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you lemons in soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In soy sauce?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.84,0:23:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: The Fist of Love! Intercept it, A Maiden's Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:20.06,Preview Title,,0,0,0,,The Fist of Love! Intercept it, A Maiden's Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
